{"tid":860440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：希望劉小麗兩年後有令人信服改變","createTime":"2018-10-13T10:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T15:09:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d35ba6645f1a18933ffe6d5bbb0382cf07a7b80d","tid":860440,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181013/s00001/3df7a3a6b57eb5bd3835e4ee81c17495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181013%2Fs00001%2F3df7a3a6b57eb5bd3835e4ee81c17495.jpg&h=51ee50e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報名參加立法會九龍西補選的工黨劉小麗，昨晚被選舉主任正式裁定其提名無效，取消其參選資格（DQ）。行政會議成員兼資深大律師湯家驊昨晚在其fb留言道：「當天她作『龜速』宣誓時，應預料到今天的結果；希望她兩年後有真的、令人信服的改變，可以重新參選。」<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊昨回覆明報時另表示，選舉主任今次沒給機會劉小麗申辯，只是參照法庭去年裁定劉小麗宣誓無效，喪失就任立法會議員資格時的理據，不應妄下結論稱劉小麗會「被終身剝削參選權利」。湯解釋，選舉主任是質疑劉小麗補選前才改變其政綱總綱，是否足以反映她真誠擁護基本法；如劉小麗未來兩年經常表現真誠擁護基本法，2020年再參選時，選舉主任未必會不信納。<br />\n<br />\n其他已報名參加今次立法會九龍西補選的，有陳凱欣、馮檢基和李卓人。"},{"pid":"35ca5c99c919b52f7d64af1150b20957d9123592","tid":860440,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181013/s00001/3dfbfcfaca4422f5e155d3e73b902ba7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181013%2Fs00001%2F3dfbfcfaca4422f5e155d3e73b902ba7.jpg&h=27d9455c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6321f91296760e5de225bb62e9cf570850862766","tid":860440,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181013/s00001/1539420321456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181013%2Fs00001%2F1539420321456&d=KJQsMM9YH0xIEYa4drRNqcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=57e72ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2F